{"tid":403537,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"操英語女子 撕中大民主牆單張　坐車離開 司機高呼「英國走狗」","createTime":"2017-09-17T09:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T05:18:19.000Z","uid":47714,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae8df6bb78db8658282f974d48041898a8da201a","tid":403537,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T09:28:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170917/s00001/1505628794557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F1505628794557&d=GGGiYPPtA8EOj5XwuKnxk3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=c262d31f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F1505628794557&h=0710117f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170917/s00001/1505628794557</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170917/s00001/908edfd0dd412145ecbfe6adc6271b6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F908edfd0dd412145ecbfe6adc6271b6f.jpg&h=9f0105c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170917/s00001/9041cac8cc2173a19a5ccfcece20b3b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F9041cac8cc2173a19a5ccfcece20b3b1.jpg&h=d6925d5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中文大學校長沈祖堯日前公開要求學生會盡快移除與「港獨」的宣傳品，否則校方會主動移除。記者今午約1時巡視民主牆，未見有新標語，另文化廣場的橫額亦未被移走，惟下午約1時20分，先後有3名人士撕下民主牆上印有「拒絕沉淪，唯有獨立」的單張。<br />\n<br />\n首先撕走紙張的為一操普通話男士，他未有回應是否中大學生或學生職員。被問為何撕走單張及是否不同意當中內容，該男士表示「我同意呀，所以才撕掉」。<br />\n<br />\n而另一位撕走單張的男士，記者表明身分上前詢問原因，該男士回應「我見有人撕走」，又指自己是「公眾人士」，因不贊成單張內容而撕走。問及擅自撕走民主牆上單張可能違法，該男士指「他們（張貼標語者）也犯法」，又說不介意目擊者報警。<br />\n<br />\n隨後一名白衣女士突然大幅度撕走民主牆上的標語，正在當值的學生會外務秘書李文耀即上前阻止並詢問身分，該女士未有回應，其後乘坐私人座駕離開。約2分鐘後，其座駕駛回現場，司機開窗並大叫「英國走狗」。<br />\n<br />\n李文耀批評撕走標語者行為，「不文明及野蠻的行為，若不滿可向學生會反映，而不是擅自撕走」。他指事出突然，將與其他幹事商討跟進方法。"},{"pid":"b8a4e1e71104beec1fd392cdaadf8816e7e043df","tid":403537,"uid":22808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T09:46:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母奶共死全家</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea5057b0f0743b852984ccf4e3ae83602bf0a6a0","tid":403537,"uid":146767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T09:48:36.000Z","msg":"咁鍾意大6就死撚返大6啦 死8婆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTG ip8+/ ipX 炒賣群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/iphonegroup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fiphonegroup&d=GGGiYPPtA8EOj5XwuKnxk3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=706aa76e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/iphonegroup</a>"},{"pid":"3a292b7428a62dbd62cdfe8bd600fc4d73b059f8","tid":403537,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T09:49:52.000Z","msg":"cusu 唔玩刑毀, 所以守黎都係嘥氣"},{"pid":"d164da4c37dc0e16e98d9a6268b912593a12d11b","tid":403537,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc26ab8a115eb1cdfdb8d3a19dd597eebd15432e","tid":403537,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:18:19.000Z","msg":"睇下五毛三色貓講左啲咩？<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r76cfn9e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr76cfn9e&h=a199a4b6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}